  <title translate="true">Views Pane_Summary</title>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal Head"><text styleclass="Normal Head" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="Program Feature" translate="true">Views Pane</text><text styleclass="Normal Head" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> s</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">hows a list of the view resources attached to the currently selected class. Double-clicking one of these views will open it for editing in the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="View_Composer" styleclass="Program Feature" translate="true">View Composer</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal Head"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">There is also a context menu providing other view-related operations.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Notes"><text styleclass="Notes" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="Notes" translate="true">Views Pane</text><text styleclass="Notes" translate="true"> is a class browser plug-in and is implemented by the </text><text styleclass="Notes" translate="true">ResourceListPlugIn</text><text styleclass="Notes" translate="true"> class in the image.</text></para>
  </body>
